Loyalty bonus: 
From the 6th to the 10th policy anniversaries: Loyalty bonus=0.5% x The average calendar month-end account value for the 12 months prior to the relevant policy anniversary on which the loyalty bonus is payable; 
On the 11th policy anniversary and thereafter: Loyalty bonus=0.9% x The average calendar month-end account value for the 12 months prior to the relevant policy anniversary on which the loyalty bonus is payable
